data.description: Approaching this extraordinary Barndominium, you'll be captivated by its classic yet contemporary design. The exterior showcases a fusion of wood and metal, with a high coffered ceiling that adds an air of grandeur. The property is full of lush greenery, ensuring privacy and a sense of escape from the hustle and bustle of city life, yet still within a 10 minute drive to the amenities of Poplar Bluff.  Inside you'll be greeted by an expansive open-concept living space combining the rustic aesthetics of a barn with modern amenities of a luxury home. Featuring two generously sized bedrooms. Each having their own private balconies and sharing a luxurious spa-like bathroom featuring a soaking tub, a separate shower, and elegant finishes. Car enthusiasts and hobbyists will be in awe of the 1500-sq ft garage, offering ample space for multiple vehicles, storage, or workshop needs and even has a saferoom for storms or storage. The covered wrap around patio lets you enjoy your 13+/-acre estate
